> [#Indonesia](https://twitter.com/hashtag/Indonesia?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw)
> gov ‘condemns’ US recognition of
> [#Jerusalem](https://twitter.com/hashtag/Jerusalem?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw)
